{"id":96062,"date":"2025-07-31T12:00:56","date_gmt":"2025-07-31T06:30:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=96062"},"modified":"2026-04-22T12:39:18","modified_gmt":"2026-04-22T07:09:18","slug":"mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca","title":{"rendered":"MBA vs MCA: Which is Better for Your Career?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_82_2 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Why_the_MBA_vs_MCA_Decision_Matters_Today\" >Why the MBA vs MCA Decision Matters Today<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#What_is_an_MBA_Degree\" >What is an MBA Degree?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#What_is_an_MCA_Degree\" >What is an MCA Degree?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_Syllabus_vs_MCA_Syllabus\" >MBA Syllabus vs MCA Syllabus<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_vs_MCA_Top_Specializations_Offered\" >MBA vs MCA: Top Specializations Offered<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_vs_MCA_for_Different_Career_Paths\" >MBA vs MCA for Different Career Paths<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#For_Corporate_Jobs\" >For Corporate Jobs<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#For_Government_Exams\" >For Government Exams<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_vs_MCA_Course_Duration_Eligibility_Top_Job_Roles\" >MBA vs MCA: Course Duration, Eligibility &amp; Top Job Roles<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Skills_Acquired_Through_MBA_and_MCA\" >Skills Acquired Through MBA and MCA<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Skills_Acquired_Through_MBA\" >Skills Acquired Through MBA:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Skills_Acquired_Through_MCA\" >Skills Acquired Through MCA:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Which_Course_Builds_Job-Ready_Skills_Faster\" >Which Course Builds Job-Ready Skills Faster?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#The_MBA_Advantage\" >The MBA Advantage:&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#The_MCA_Advantage\" >The MCA Advantage:&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Role_of_Internships_Certifications_in_MBA_and_MCA\" >Role of Internships &amp; Certifications in MBA and MCA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_vs_MCA_Career_Opportunities\" >MBA vs MCA: Career Opportunities<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MBA_Career_Opportunities\" >MBA Career Opportunities&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#MCA_Career_Opportunities\" >MCA Career Opportunities<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-20\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Salary_Comparison_MBA_vs_MCA\" >Salary Comparison: MBA vs MCA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-21\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Higher_Studies_After_MBA_and_MCA\" >Higher Studies After MBA and MCA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-22\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Common_Myths_About_MBA_and_MCA\" >Common Myths About MBA and MCA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-23\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#Conclusion\" >Conclusion<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-24\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\/#FAQs\" >FAQs<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>Unsure about what line of study to pursue at the postgraduate level. Both the MBA and the MCA are popular choices for many students graduating with a Bachelor\u2019s degree. The choice between the two largely depends on your academic interests, strengths, and career goals.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While an MBA unlocks pathways to business roles and senior leadership positions, an MCA can help develop deep technical expertise, facilitating faster entry into high-paying tech roles in the IT sector.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Answering the question, MBA or MCA, which is better, becomes easier when you know the one that best aligns with your future career aspirations. We further help you make an informed decision in this blog. Read on to know more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_the_MBA_vs_MCA_Decision_Matters_Today\"><\/span><strong>Why the MBA vs MCA Decision Matters Today<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The decision between MBA and MCA among undergraduates is more relevant today than ever before. This is largely due to the rapid evolution of industries driven by both business innovation and digital transformation:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>The career outcomes differ significantly:<\/strong> While an MBA often paves the way for senior management and leadership positions, an MCA is a stepping stone to IT-oriented and tech roles.<br><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Shift in industry demand:<\/strong> Organizations today need professionals who have both core technical proficiencies and strategic business leadership to drive employees toward achieving common business objectives. Hence, the confusion between MBA and MCA courses is inevitable.<br>&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Future career growth and earning potential:<\/strong> Making the right choice between the two programs can unlock global career prospects, fast-track promotions, and boost graduates&#8217; salary potential.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_an_MBA_Degree\"><\/span><strong>What is an MBA Degree?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we initiate the discussion on MCA or MBA, which is better, let\u2019s begin by defining what an MBA degree entails.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A Master of Business Administration (MBA) is a business management degree program offered by many universities at the postgraduate level. The program&#8217;s primary focus is equipping learners with skills in management, leadership, and strategic decision-making to facilitate career progression. The degree is thus ideal for (and highly preferred by) senior working professionals in multiple industries.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the key study areas in an MBA program include marketing, finance, operations, entrepreneurship, and human resources. Professionals aspiring to enter executive or managerial positions or launch their own business generally pursue an MBA.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The program focuses heavily on case studies, real-world applications, and student networking, preparing them for dynamic business roles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_an_MCA_Degree\"><\/span><strong>What is an MCA Degree?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MCA is the popular acronym for Master of Computer Applications, a postgraduate degree offered to aspiring learners of advanced software development, computer science, and IT systems. The program is designed to equip students with specialized skills in database management, programming, application design, and networking.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An MCA is considered ideal for those aiming to establish high-paying careers in data analysis, software development, or IT consulting. Strong emphasis is placed on imparting industry-relevant and hands-on knowledge and skills in the domain.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_Syllabus_vs_MCA_Syllabus\"><\/span><strong>MBA Syllabus vs MCA Syllabus<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To better understand and answer\u2014<strong>MBA or MCA, which has more scope \u2014<\/strong>let us take a closer look at the course curricula of the two disciplines.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Semesters<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><br><br><strong>1st Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>Entrepreneurial Practice<br>Business Communication (WAC)<br>Managerial Economics<br>Financial Accounting<br>Data Visualization (Excel\/Tableau)<br>Organizational Behavior<br>Marketing Management<\/td><td>Fundamentals of Computers and IT<br>Fundamentals of Mathematics<br>Discrete Mathematics and Graph Theory<br>Python Programming<br>Programming and Problem Solving in C<br>Relational Database <br>Management System<br>Data Visualization<br>Relational Database Management Systems &#8211; Lab<br>Programming and Problem Solving in C &#8211; Lab&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Python Programming &#8211; Lab<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>2nd Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>Business Research Methods (R\/Python)<br>Operation Management<br>Human Resource Management<br>Management Accounting<br>Financial Management<br>Legal Aspects of Business<br>Business Communication (VAC)&nbsp;<\/td><td><strong>Core Subjects<\/strong><br>Computer Networks and Protocols<br>Object-Oriented Programming Using Java<br>Operating System<br>Data Structure and Algorithms<br>Computer Architecture<br>Object-Oriented Programming using Java &#8211; Lab<br>Data Structure and Algorithms &#8211; Lab<br>Elective-I<br><br><strong>Elective\/Specialization<\/strong><br>AI &amp; Data Science<br>Cloud Computing<br>Cyber Security<br>Comprehensive Emerging Technologies<br>AI &amp; ML<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>3rd Semester<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Core Subjects<\/strong><br>Strategic Management<br>Term Paper<br>4 modules as per chosen elective<br><br><strong>Specialization\/Elective<\/strong><br><strong>Super\/Dual (Choose Any One)<\/strong><br><br>Digital Marketing<br>Finance&nbsp;<br>Marketing&nbsp;<br>HRM<br>Analytics &amp; DS<br>BFSI<br>IT &amp; FinTech<br>Operations Management<br>International Business<br>Information System Management<br>Project Management<br>Supply Chain Management<br>Retail Management<\/td><td><strong>Core Subjects<\/strong><br>Unix and Shell Programming<br>Web Technology<br>Software Engineering and Project Management<br>Unix and Shell Programming &#8211; Lab<br>Web Technology &#8211; Lab<br>Elective-II<br>Elective-III<br><br><strong>Elective\/Specialization:<\/strong><br>AI &amp; Data Science<br>Cloud Computing\u00a0<br>Cyber Security<br>Comprehensive Emerging Technologies<br>AI &amp; ML<br><br><br><br><br><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><strong>4th Semester<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Core Subjects<\/strong><br>International Business Management<br>Project<br>4 modules as per chosen elective<br><br><strong>Specialization:<\/strong><br>Digital Marketing<br>Finance&nbsp;<br>Marketing&nbsp;<br>HRM<br>Analytics &amp; DS<br>BFSI<br>IT &amp; FinTech<br>Operations Management<br>International Business<br>Information System Management<br>Project Management<br>Supply Chain Management<br>Retail Management<\/td><td><strong>Core Subjects<\/strong><br>Mobile Application Development<br>Project Work<br>Elective-IV<br><br><strong>Elective\/Specialization:<\/strong><br>AI &amp; Data Science<br>Cloud Computing\u00a0<br>Cyber Security<br>Comprehensive Emerging Technologies<br>AI &amp; ML<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_vs_MCA_Top_Specializations_Offered\"><\/span><strong>MBA vs MCA: Top Specializations Offered<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When deciding between an MBA and MCA, it makes sense to explore the specializations each course offers. After all, these electives or specializations pave the final way for the future career paths of graduates in the two programs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>MBA Specializations<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA Specializations<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-finance\">MBA in Finance<\/a>: <\/strong>Helps you master core finance skills &#8211; accounting, numerical proficiency, quantitative abilities.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-human-resource-management\">MBA in HRM<\/a>: <\/strong>Enables you to gain domain expertise and master essential HR practices.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-analytics-data-science\">MBA in Analytics &amp; Data Science<\/a>: <\/strong>Provides a strong foundation for cross-sectoral roles via a comprehensive curriculum covering exploratory data analysis, advanced ML, and programming in data science. <strong>\u00a0<\/strong>\u00a0<br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-project-management\"><strong>MBA in<\/strong> <strong>Project Management<\/strong><\/a><strong>: <\/strong>Helps pave the way for increased earning potential for graduates by providing specialized knowledge in the field.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-marketing\">MBA in Marketing<\/a>: <\/strong>An opportunity to hone your marketing skills in market research, strategic thinking, analysis, and brand management.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-international-business\">MBA in International Business<\/a>: <\/strong>Paves the way for a secure, high-paying career path through mastering core subjects in international business and specialized skills in the domain.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-operations-management\">MBA in Operations Management<\/a>: <\/strong>Builds comprehensive domain knowledge through key subjects and best practices in essential operations management functions.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-supply-chain-management\">MBA in Supply Chain Management<\/a>: <\/strong>A chance to gain diverse skillsets in logistics management, supply chain operations, and supplier relationship management.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-banking-financial-services-insurance\">MBA in BFSI<\/a>: <\/strong>A chance to learn the sought-after skills in the banking, financial services, and insurance sectors by enhancing your financial acumen.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-it-fintech\">MBA in IT &amp; FinTech<\/a>: <\/strong>Enables you to build a rewarding career path in an emerging field by acquiring a deep understanding of IT and finance concepts.\u00a0<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-information-system-management\">MBA in Information System Management<\/a>: <\/strong>Offers specialized knowledge and learning in computer networks, software engineering, and technology management.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-retail-management\">MBA in Retail Management<\/a>: <\/strong>Enables accelerated career progression opportunities for graduates in the evolving retail segment and a chance to enter senior management and leadership roles.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mba-digital-marketing\">MBA in Digital Marketing<\/a>: <\/strong>Provides learners with an exclusive opportunity to boost their digital proficiency by acquiring a deep understanding of the essentials of digital marketing.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/td><td><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-ai-and-data-science-muj\">MCA in AI &amp; Data Science<\/a>: <\/strong>Allows you to advance your career in these fields by mastering the in-demand technical skills and deepening your knowledge in the tech landscape.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-cloud-computing-muj\">MCA in Cloud Computing<\/a>: <\/strong>A chance to level up your career in cloud computing by developing essential skills and gaining in-depth knowledge in database management, programming, and cloud virtualization architectures.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-cyber-security-muj\">MCA in Cybersecurity<\/a>: <\/strong>Allows you to transform your career trajectory by honing key technical skills in risk management, network security, and threat intelligence.\u00a0<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-comprehensive-emerging-technologies-muj\">MCA in Comprehensive Emerging Technologies<\/a>: <\/strong>An opportunity to develop expertise in the emerging technologies and hone new-age skills in blockchain, IoT, data mining, and more.<br><br><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-mca-ai-and-machine-learning-muj\">MCA in AI &amp; ML<\/a>: <\/strong>Helps you prepare for a rewarding future in AI innovation by letting you master essential AI &amp; ML skills in NLP, neural networks, and reinforcement learning.\u00a0\u00a0<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_vs_MCA_for_Different_Career_Paths\"><\/span><strong>MBA vs MCA for Different Career Paths<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The choice between an MBA and an MCA also becomes easier depending on whether you aspire for business management or leadership positions in your industry or technical expertise in your domain. To help you in your decision, we list below the various career paths that both MBA and MCA open up in different sectors:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"For_Corporate_Jobs\"><\/span><strong>For Corporate Jobs<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Career Paths<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA&nbsp;<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><br><br><strong>Job Roles<\/strong><\/td><td>Management Consultant<br>Financial Analyst<br>Marketing Manager<br>Operations Manager<br>HR Manager<\/td><td>Software Developer<br>Data Scientist<br>Cloud Architect<br>Cybersecurity Specialist<br>DevOps Engineer<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><strong>Hiring Industries<\/strong><\/td><td>Management Consulting<br>Banking\/FinTech<br>Technology&nbsp;<br>FMCG<br>E-Commerce&nbsp;<\/td><td>IT Services<br>Product and Technology&nbsp;<br>Banking\/Finance<br>Cloud\/AI&nbsp;E-Commerce&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>For Entrepreneurship<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Career Paths<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><br><br><strong>Job Roles<\/strong><\/td><td>Startup Founder<br>Product Manager<br>Business Consultant<br>Venture Capital Analyst<br>Business Development Manager<\/td><td>Full Stack Developer<br>Cloud Architect<br>AI\/ML Engineer<br>IT Consultant<br>Product Manager<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><strong>Hiring Industries<\/strong><\/td><td>Technology&nbsp;<br>E-Commerce<br>Consulting&nbsp;<br>Finance<br>Venture Capital<\/td><td>FinTech<br>IT Services<br>E-Commerce\/Logistics<br>Software <br>Product Development<br>Cybersecurity&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"For_Government_Exams\"><\/span><strong>For Government Exams<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Career Paths<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><br><br><strong>Scope<\/strong><\/td><td>PSU Management Officer<br>RBI Grade B Officer<br>Public Sector Bank Manager<br>Taluk Development Officer<br>SEBI Grade A Officer&nbsp;<\/td><td>Scientist\/Technical Officer (DRDO, ISRO, NIC)<br>IT Officer<br>Programmer<br>Cybersecurity Analyst<br>System Analyst<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><strong>Hiring Industries<\/strong><\/td><td>PSUs<br>BFSI<br>Logistics &amp; Railways<br>Civil Services<br>SEBI\/NABARD\/RBI<\/td><td>PSUs<br>DRDO<br>Banking&nbsp;<br>NIC<br>Indian Railways<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_vs_MCA_Course_Duration_Eligibility_Top_Job_Roles\"><\/span><strong>MBA vs MCA: Course Duration, Eligibility &amp; Top Job Roles<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One other way to determine whether an MCA or an MBA is better after a BCA is to compare the two programs&#8217; durations, admission criteria, and leading job opportunities for graduates.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Parameters<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Course duration<\/strong><\/td><td>24 months (2 years) \/ 4 semesters<\/td><td>24 months (2 years) \/ 4 semesters<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><br><br><br><strong>Eligibility criteria<\/strong><\/td><td>Completion of a 10+2+3-year Bachelor\u2019s degree from a recognized university\/institution<br><br>An equivalent qualification as recognized by the Association of Indian Universities (AIU)<br><br>A minimum of 50% marks in aggregate in graduation (45% for students from reserved categories)<\/td><td>Completion of 10+2+3-year Bachelor\u2019s degree in Computer Applications\/Computer Science\/IT from a recognized university\/institution&nbsp;<br><br>An equivalent qualification as recognized by AIU or other competent bodies<br><br>Candidates who completed a 10+2+3-year Bachelor\u2019s degree from other streams like Science, Business Administration, Business Management, Arts &amp; Humanities, Commerce, etc., are also eligible for MCA admission, but need to attend and complete a compulsory bridge course in fundamentals of computer and IT, along with their Semester 1 courses<br><br>Candidates without a Mathematics background in their 10 + 2\/Bachelor\u2019s degree programs must attend and complete a compulsory bridge course in Mathematics along with other Semester 1 courses<br><br>A minimum of 50% marks in aggregate in graduation (45% for students from reserved categories)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><br><strong>Top job roles<\/strong><\/td><td>Digital Marketing Manager<br>Brand Manager<br>Product Marketing Manager<br>Portfolio Manager<br>Supply Chain Manager<\/td><td>Full Stack Developer<br>Software Developer<br>Data Scientist<br>Cloud Solutions <br>Architect<br>Database Administrator<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Skills_Acquired_Through_MBA_and_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Skills Acquired Through MBA and MCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Both MCA and MBA courses impart specialized skills to students, helping them build rewarding career paths. Some of the top skills developed through each of the programs are listed below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Skills_Acquired_Through_MBA\"><\/span><strong>Skills Acquired Through MBA:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Knowledge of finance, marketing, and operations&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Team management and leadership<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Business planning and entrepreneurship<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Strategic thinking and decision-making<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Effective communication and interpersonal skills<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Skills_Acquired_Through_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Skills Acquired Through MCA:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>&nbsp;Data structures and database management<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Programming languages such as Python, Java, and C++<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Analytical thinking and problem-solving ability<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>System design and software development<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Web and mobile app development<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Which_Course_Builds_Job-Ready_Skills_Faster\"><\/span><strong>Which Course Builds Job-Ready Skills Faster?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Continuing the discussion on whether an MBA or an MCA is better, let us now analyze which of the two courses can prepare students for the job market faster. While an MCA typically prepares learners more quickly for technical roles by imparting industry-ready skills, an MBA may require more practical exposure through internships and projects to become job-ready.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_MBA_Advantage\"><\/span><strong>The MBA Advantage:&nbsp;<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Exposure via case studies<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Strong industry readiness through internships&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Experience in real-world business environments<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_MCA_Advantage\"><\/span><strong>The MCA Advantage:&nbsp;<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Facilitates immediate employment in the IT sector via experience through projects, coding, and technical expertise<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Emphasis on niche emerging technologies such as cybersecurity, AI, and web development, enabling targeted entry into specific IT roles<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Offers advanced learning in industry-relevant tools and technologies, such as exposure to IDEs, frameworks, and modern tech stacks<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Role_of_Internships_Certifications_in_MBA_and_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Role of Internships &amp; Certifications in MBA and MCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Internships and certifications play a vital role in helping students bridge the gap between academic learning and real-world job roles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>MBA students can avail themselves of internship opportunities to gain valuable hands-on experience in the real business world. Add-on certifications help them gain expertise in specific areas such as marketing, finance, or analytics.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For MCA students, technical internships and certifications, such as those in cloud computing, programming, and cybersecurity, help validate the skills they have earned and improve industry readiness.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Both internships and certifications are vital for strengthening students\u2019 resumes, improving their job prospects, and expanding their professional networks.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_vs_MCA_Career_Opportunities\"><\/span><strong>MBA vs MCA: Career Opportunities<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To find out more about MBA or MCA, which has more scope, let\u2019s take a close look at the career prospects that both courses unlock for their graduates:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MBA_Career_Opportunities\"><\/span><strong>MBA Career Opportunities<\/strong><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Job Roles<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Hiring Industries<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Digital Marketing Manager<\/td><td>Hospitals &amp; Healthcare<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Brand Manager<\/td><td>IT\/ITeS<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Product Marketing Manager<\/td><td>Banks &amp; Financial Institutions<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Portfolio Manager<\/td><td>FMCG<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Supply Chain Manager<\/td><td>EdTech\/FinTech<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"MCA_Career_Opportunities\"><\/span><strong>MCA Career Opportunities<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Job Roles<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Hiring Industries<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Full Stack Developer<\/td><td>Cybersecurity&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Software Engineer<\/td><td>Cloud Computing<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Data Analyst<\/td><td>E-Commerce<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Cloud Architect<\/td><td>Gaming<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Database Engineer<\/td><td>Learning &amp; Academia<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Salary_Comparison_MBA_vs_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Salary Comparison: MBA vs MCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A quick peek at the earning potential of MBA and MCA graduates also helps you decide which program to pursue for a long-term, rewarding career path.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Career Level<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MBA Graduates&nbsp;<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA Graduates<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Entry-level \/ fresher (0-3 years)<\/td><td>INR 3 LPA &#8211; INR 10 LPA (approx)<\/td><td>INR 3 LPA &#8211; INR 8 LPA (approx)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Mid-level (4-7 years)<\/td><td>INR 10 LPA &#8211; INR 15 LPA (approx)<\/td><td>INR 10 LPA &#8211; INR 18 LPA (approx)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Senior-level (8+ years)<\/td><td>INR 15 LPA &#8211; INR 20 LPA (approx)<\/td><td>INR 20 LPA &#8211; INR 35 LPA+ (approx)<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: Geeks for Geeks, Jooble<\/em>, <em>LPU<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Higher_Studies_After_MBA_and_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Higher Studies After MBA and MCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The prospect of higher learning helps MBA and MCA graduates advance their knowledge in their respective domains and boost their career prospects.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Higher Study Options After MBA:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Executive MBA<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>PhD in Management<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Specialized certifications, such as in Marketing, Finance, or Data Analytics<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Higher Study Options After MCA:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>PhD in Computer Science<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>M.Tech<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add-on certifications in Data Science, AI, and Cybersecurity<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Common_Myths_About_MBA_and_MCA\"><\/span><strong>Common Myths About MBA and MCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While analyzing MBA vs MCA, which is the best, let\u2019s also look at some common myths that students have about the two courses and make an attempt to bust them to help you make an informed choice:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>MBA Common Myths<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>MCA Common Myths<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>1) An MBA assures instant success.<br><br><strong><em>Reality:<\/em><\/strong> Success after any course depends on work experience, skills, and individual effort.<br><br>2) An MBA is only for students with a business background.<br><br><strong><em>Reality:<\/em><\/strong> Students from any background can pursue an MBA.<br><br>3) An MBA is only useful for working at big corporations.<br><br><strong><em>Reality:<\/em><\/strong> The degree holds value in entrepreneurship ventures, startups, and NGOs.<\/td><td>1) MCA has a limited career scope\u00a0<br><br><strong><em>Reality:<\/em><\/strong> MCA graduates can find multiple opportunities in data science, AI, and cybersecurity sectors.<br><br>2) MCA is only about coding all day long.<br><br><strong>Reality<\/strong>: MCA prepares you for roles in management, system design, and a wide range of IT roles.<br><br>3) Only Math experts can pursue an MCA.\u00a0<br><br><strong><em>Reality:<\/em><\/strong> A mathematics background may not be mandatory in all universities, as some institutions allow bridge courses. However, basic logical and quantitative aptitude is highly helpful.<br><br><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Conclusion\"><\/span><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The choice between MCA and MBA, which is better after a BCA, largely depends on which of the two programs best aligns with your overall passion and career goals. If entering leadership roles or experiencing business growth is your ultimate aim, an MBA is ideal. However, an MCA is better suited to developing mastery in technical roles.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Manipal University Jaipur offers students the opportunity to pursue both MBA and MCA programs as per their interests on the Online Manipal platform. Choose the one that you are committed to for your career path and experience its numerous benefits, including the option to study in 100% online mode while continuing your other academic or professional commitments.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FAQs\"><\/span><strong>FAQs <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Which is better, MBA or MCA?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There is no single option that is \u201cbetter\u201d than the other. The choice between the two depends on your overall career objectives. An MBA may offer faster business growth opportunities, while an MCA offers a stable, high-paying technical career path.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. What is the difference between an MBA and an MCA?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The key difference between the two courses lies in their overall approach. While an MBA focuses broadly on business management and prepares learners for leadership roles across varied industries, an MCA focuses on imparting deep technical expertise for high-paying careers in technology.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Which course has better career opportunities, MBA or MCA?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both programs offer excellent career prospects after graduation. An MBA paves the way for management and leadership roles, while an MCA is more suitable for tech-oriented careers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. Which has a higher salary, MBA or MCA?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Graduates of both programs are likely to have high earning potential, depending on their skills, work experience, and other factors. An MBA graduate may earn high owing to the repute of the institution they graduate from (top-tier B-schools), while an MCA graduate may bridge this gap through their experience and specialized skills.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Which course is easier, MBA or MCA?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The difficulty level of any program may vary from one student to another. Students with strong analytical and communication skills may find an MBA easier, while those with a strong technical background may find pursuing an MCA simpler.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Unsure about what line of study to pursue at the postgraduate level. Both the MBA and the MCA are popular choices for many students graduating with a Bachelor\u2019s degree. The choice between the two largely depends on your academic interests, strengths, and career goals.&nbsp; While an MBA unlocks pathways to business roles and senior leadership [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":126,"featured_media":17284660,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[605,607],"tags":[31,14,18],"class_list":["post-96062","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mba","category-mca","tag-online-bca","tag-online-mba","tag-online-mca"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>MBA vs MCA: Which is Better for Your Career?<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"MBA vs MCA: Understand scope, salary, career paths, and skills to choose the right course for your future.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/96062\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"MBA vs MCA: Which is Better for Your Career?\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MBA vs MCA: Understand scope, salary, career paths, and skills to choose the right course for your future.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-option-after-bca\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2025-07-31T06:30:56+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2026-04-22T07:09:18+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/MBA-or-MCA_-Which-is-better-after-BCA.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"980\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"380\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Krishnanjali KU\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"Written by\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1\" content=\"Krishnanjali KU\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:label2\" content=\"Estimated reading time\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data2\" content=\"5 minutes\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/mba-or-mca-which-is-a-better-op